title: Podcast: 'Triple Option' reviews Week 7, looks ahead to Week 8 of prep football
text:
By Jeff Johnson , Jeff Linder and K.J. Pilcher , The Gazette October 14, 2015 | 2:43 pm 
The Gazette's Jeff Linder, Jeff Johnson and K.J. Pilcher review the past week of prep football and look ahead to upcoming games in Eastern Iowa in the latest edition of the Triple Option Podcast. Your browser does not support the audio element. Your Next Prep Football Articles
